snippet.title: [Goblin BGM] 운명 (Fate) Piano Cover
snippet.description:
Piano Cover of one of Goblin's soundtracks, "Fate".
(Grim Reaper Theme -- I don't know the actual name of the song since it's yet to be released officially so I named it myself XD. Also known as "The Path Of The Deceased")
I was worried that I might ruin this gorgeous piece if I had done anything to it, so I haven't done any arrangements for this one.
Enjoy :)

드라마 도깨비 BGM 중 하나인 "운명" (망자의 길 / 저승사자 테마곡) 피아노 커버입니다. 
아직 정식 OST 음원들이 안풀려서 제목은 제가 마음대로 지어봤어요 ㅎㅎ
